  "description": "<i>Hero's Saga: Laevatein Tactics</i> is a fantasy themed 2D tactical role-playing game played from a bird's-eye perspective. The game is set on the fictional continent of Yulanecca and starts with the young prince Ernesto (or the name the player chooses) of Valencia receiving a powerful blade to defeat an undead host besieging a border fortress. <br><br>In the game the player has to move his hero across the map over a grid in a turn based manner. The player can occupy bases on the map and attack enemy units if in range. If an enemy is encountered the game will enter a battle mode in which the player and his army has to defeat the opposing army. The player can choose to attack, charge, defend or phalanx. The players forces can be replenished at a stronghold.",
